<h2 data-block-key="rnmbw">The Foolish bottom line</h2><p data-block-key="01ptl">Investing money may seem intimidating, especially if you’ve never done it before. However, if you figure out <b>1.</b> how you want to invest, <b>2.</b> how much money you should invest, and <b>3.</b> your risk tolerance, you&#x27;ll be well positioned to make smart decisions with your money that will serve you well for decades to come.</p>
